title: KUNMI Women's Ripped Mid Waisted Boyfriend Jeans Loose Fit Distressed Stretchy Denim Pants
description: KUNMI womens ripped jeans is made with lightweight and soft denim super stretch material, which are flexible and breathable, comfortable to wear. Even after repeated wearing, this denim stays true to original form.

Casual relaxed fitting jeans with ripped detailing, 5 traditional pockets, zip fly and button closure. Ripped denim jean pants for women with soft, breathable, durable and stretchy denim fabric for everyday comfort.

This jeans pants easy to pair with all tops from fashionable to basic T-shirts and all footwear from stylish boots to your favorite shoes. Keep your look trendy and laid back by wearing these fashion.
Wash recommended with cold water/do not bleach/hang or line dry/wash with like colours,that will increase the durability of your denim jeans.
